<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TKT10">
<l>cittamuñ cevvai nillā teñceykēṉ tīvi ṉaiyēṉ</l>
<l>pattimaik kaṉpu ṭaiyē ṉāvatē paṇiyā yentāy</l>
<l>muttoḷi marata kamē muḻaṅkoḷi mukilvaṇ ṇāyeṉ</l>
<l>attaniṉ ṉaṭimai yallāl yātumoṉ ṟaṟiki lēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even my mind won’t stay on track; what can I, of evil karma, do?</l>
<l>Grant that I have love for devoutness [to you], my father,</l>
<l>[My] pearl, brilliant emerald, you the hue of [lightning-]lit thunder clouds.</l>
<l>My Father, besides service to you, I am not capable of knowing anything.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
